data.description: I know what I'm asking Santa for this year for Christmas! A fabulous home in West Conway with a POOL! What better way to start the new year off than with a stunning three bedroom/two bath, craftsman style home, built in 2019. This home is made for entertaining with a covered back porch, grilling patio & built in seating around the pool! The backyard is completely fenced in and there is a Ring security alarm system around the house. This home has fabulous curb appeal being located on a corner lot. Walking to the front door, you will notice the wooden shutters, flower beds & a spacious covered front porch. As you enter the home, you will walk into the entry way which leads into an open floor plan living room, kitchen & dining area. This home has a split floorpan with the en-suite being located on the right past the mud room, laundry room & garage door entrance. There is a built in safe in the primary closet & a huge walk in shower, as well as a tub. On the left side of this home, you will find the other two spacious bedrooms with walk in closets & another fabulous bathroom. In the garage is a tankless hot water heater, tornado storm shelter & irrigation system. Agents see remarks.
